/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling city street, bathed in the soft glow of a bright blue sky. The sun, high in the heavens, casts a warm light that illuminates the scene. The street is lined with towering buildings, their glass facades reflecting the radiant sunlight. Cars, painted in various hues, are scattered across the street, their metallic bodies gleaming under the sun's rays. Trees, their leaves a vibrant green, provide a touch of nature amidst the urban landscape. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, forming a complex web that connects the city's inhabitants. The perspective of the image is from a low angle, looking up at the towering buildings and the expansive sky, giving a sense of scale and grandeur to the cityscape.
